data.description: Introducing Unit 103 at 4141 N Henderson Rd, Arlington, VA – A Luxurious Haven in the Heart of Arlington! Nestled in the prestigious Hyde Park neighborhood, this splendid unit promises a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort and sophistication. Spanning 1170 square feet, this thoughtfully designed apartment offers an open-concept layout, making the most of its space. Its design is the perfect blend of contemporary aesthetics with its exposed columns and timeless functionality. As you step inside, you are greeted by gleaming hardwood floors and a soothing, neutral color palette. The living area is spacious and versatile, ideal for hosting friends and family or simply unwinding after a long day. Large windows bathe the space in sunlight, while providing scenic views of the surrounding neighborhood off the large balcony. The kitchen is a gourmet's delight, boasting stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and beautiful countertops that make meal preparation a breeze. Whether you're a seasoned chef or a novice cook, this kitchen is sure to inspire your culinary creativity. This unit also boasts 1.5 bathrooms with modern fixtures and finishes and multiple walk-in closets, ensuring you have ample storage space for all your belongings. The array of amenities to cater to your every need in this building include, 24/7 concierge service, a 25 meter pool, community garden and a picnic area with both gas and charcoal grills. A secure parking garage for residents, providing both convenience and peace of mind is available for a small additional fee. Situated in the heart of the Ballston area of Arlington, you are just moments away from the finest dining, shopping, and entertainment options in the area. The neighborhood is known for its friendly community and access to public transportation, making your daily commute a breeze. FHA & VA Approved Building. Assumable VA Mortgage 2.25% Current Balance - approx $316,000 Serviced by Rocket Mortgage
